snippet.title: Yunyun Syndrome!? Rhythm Psychosis | First Trailer
snippet.description:
Steam：https://store.steampowered.com/app/2914150/
📡⚡WishList now to stay updated! ⚡📡 

“Yunyun Syndrome!? Rhythm Psychosis” is a rhythm adventure game about a psychotic hikikomori girl - also an avid anonymous poster - who corrupts the world with her severe brain rot from listening to too many denpa songs.
Yun-Yun all over this world.

Denpa signals to be transmitted soon,
stay prepared for the release during 2024!
